              "note": "$\\sin 2\\theta = \\dfrac{24}{25}$"
            }
          ],
          "answer": "$\\sin 2\\theta = \\dfrac{24}{25}$",
          "solution": "$$\\sin 2\\theta = 2\\sin\\theta\\cos\\theta = 2 \\cdot \\frac45 \\cdot \\frac35 = \\frac{24}{25}.$$",
          "verify": [
